* Torrents have been taken of the 'tap' and put on disease, tons of luclin mobs are disease resistant... say anything in Umbral.... so we cant use Torrents here.<br>
     Basically Torrent of pain/hate are the same as single target buffs, Pain is an 11ac buff for all group members, Hate is 47atk buff for all group members, Fatigue adds stamina to all group members... doesnt add to many hp though (compared to divine strength etc since it's a stamina buff) but does stack with necro buff's wich is it's saveing grace.<br>
